Argued February 14 decision released March 12, 1996 *937Joseph L. Ciasen, with whom, on the brief, were David W. Bogan, John N. Thomas and Steven J. Armstrong, for the appellant (defendant). Shelley R. Sadin, with whom, on the brief, was Paul F. Thomas, for the appellee (plaintiff). PER CURIAM.
